n style=\"color: red;\">原來醬囝嘅過去係咁</span></span><br />\n<br />\n醬囝嘅悲慘過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇高登原link?</blockquote><br />\n蔣, 狗. (2016, August 19). 有冇人認識禮賢會彭學高紀念中學呢間校教合一既學校? Retrieved from 香港高登: <a href=\"http://forum1.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=ET&amp;message=6493169&amp;page=11&amp;highlight_id=0&amp;authorOnly=False\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum1.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DET%26message%3D6493169%26page%3D11%26highlight_id%3D0%26authorOnly%3DFalse&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=85ea65d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://forum1.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=ET&amp;message=6493169&amp;page=11&amp;highlight_id=0&amp;authorOnly=False</a>"},{"pid":"36eb7d48955a3a18b715701cd692bd7bee47722b","tid":225930,"uid":19493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T07:22:51.000Z","msg":"蔣式pish post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n蔣狗 : 真名叫蘇俊安, 中介事件時19歲, 住觀塘月華街40號萬福大廈10樓 (俾中介淋紅油事件新聞有報導)<br />\nDSE 1分,曾讀慕光英文書院 (觀塘區band3)俾校方踢出校<br />\n聲稱今年retake 17DSE, (不過DSE期間佢長期上黎mon post,希望佢18年DSE會背好D中文範文 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n蔣狗住址一早曝光, 祝醬仔身體健康, 合家平安 <br />\n<br />\n廢青蔣狗單位<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/69APZJC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F69APZJC.jpg&h=17a620b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/181gsG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F181gsG.jpg&h=93d860bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J95821Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ95821Y.jpg&h=47dafb41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h1gu1D1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh1gu1D1.jpg&h=ae4282b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n狗閪被起底後聲稱3小時內去左灣仔, 將軍澳同埋觀塘警局報案要搵CID告鳩D連登仔, 最後走數 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W650412.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW650412.jpg&h=8bbe4fac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"49e2d7f71e24ab3d9638df1ddc3d148ca7a4ad7c","tid":225930,"uid":23021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T07:23:39.000Z","msg":"正負皮已反應一切"},{"pid":"df15b451e8945881a38b36745d8aa976579c69c1","tid":225930,"uid":19493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T07:23:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>醬囝當年一定比人玩到好撚慘，<br />\n咁多年之後都仲記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不如你講下點樣比人玩，<br />\n如果真係過份嘅，<br />\n我地幫你拎番個公道</blockquote>"},{"pid":"0aa8b2237884649d183df0046740cc0870010fea","tid":225930,"uid":78900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T07:24:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Je Suis Confiture fiston</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>Ich bin Billy So</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"33ce90ae7222136102601a6d8ac1f98d5ee9c33c","tid":225930,"uid":19493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T07:25:11.000Z","msg":"蘇蠢戇讀邊間中學俾人踢出校？<br />\n衰咩？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color